text:
How does it feel when you try it on?
Is the size okay?

This tiara, it reminds me of
the one in a black and white movie.

It was worn by a princess from some country,
and even though it was black and white, it sparkled so much.

Oh, I see... Maybe because it doesn't have color,
it gives off a transparent vibe.

So, does it look transparent?
Me.

Yeah, of course.
You look even more transparent and radiant than usual.

Oh, that's nice.
The tiara looks great.
